<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1051494>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Oxysarcodexia catica sp. n., holotype ♂. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Terminalia, lateral view. C. Genitalia, anterior view. D. Distiphallus, anteroapical view. E. Distiphallus, anterior view. F. Terminalia, posterior view. Abbreviations: ajm = anterior juxtal margin; ce = cercus; ep = epandrium; j = juxta; ls = lateral stylus; mp = median process; pjm = posterior juxtal margin; po = postgonite; pp = paraphallus; pr = pregonite; st = syntergosternite 7 + 8; su = surstylus; ve = vesica." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1051494/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

